All Classes

  • All Classes Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    Configuration
    Configuration for Money Service HQ application.
    Currency
    This class defines a Currency object in MoneyService The currency class is a value type used to store the currency code of a currency and it's exchange rate without interest.
    HQ
    This class holds all Sites available and handles all statistics
    HQApp
    This class works as HeadQuarter for Site(s).
    MoneyServiceIO
    This class acts as a bridge between Money Service Site and Money Service HQ.
    Order
    This class defines a Order in MoneyService Order should be created by specifying site name, currency code, the amount and transaction mode, buy or sell.
    Period
    An enumeration holding values for the available periods to choose when generating statistics
    Transaction
    This class represents a transaction in the MoneyService system.
    TransactionMode
    An enumeration holding values SELL and BUY seen from the Money Service Site's perspective.
